  "texts": [
    "As expected, all composites exhibited a strong discriminatory ability between SCD and ADD individuals.",
    "They also offered a clear, although lower, differentiation of SCD and MCI subjects.",
    "Notably, the composites of executive functions, language, memory, and visuospatial functions provided the best discrimination between SCD and ADD individuals (AUC > 0.98).",
    "The attention composite showed a lower predictive performance (AUC ≈ 0.95).",
    "In the detection of MCI individuals, the values were slightly lower."
